import React from "react"; import {useState} from "react"; export default function Navbar(){ const [isActive,setIsActive] = useState(false) console.log(isActive) return(
setIsActive(!isActive)} role="button" className={`navbar-burger burger ${isActive ? 'is-active' : ''}`} aria-label="menu" aria-expanded="false" data-target="navbarBasicExample">
) }
